snippet.title: Johou Battle Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Jojo's Bizarre Adventure and Touhou Project crossover, Johou Battle, is finally here! 
Get it here: https://pinclock.itch.io/johou-battle

Johou Battle is a bullet hell shoot 'em up game  putting you in the shoes of Jotaro Kujo, the legendary fighter of Jojo's Bizarre Adventure fame or Ichirin Kumoi, a fighting spirit from Touhou Project, and pits you against the other! Take on a barrage of attacks lovingly crafted tributes to Jojo's Bizarre Adventure and Touhou Project!
